metadata.name: China 1.0  #1
metadata.description:
This collection of 5 NFTs was taken in 2018 in Dali City in Yunnan Province. Rural China portrays my view of a part of the population that is at a slower pace averse to modernization. All this to leave the question in the air. Whether technology and modernization will destroy the traditional part of China. I searched with my camera for these increasingly scarce moments in an increasingly futuristic country.

4000 x 3472 px
